  "body": {
    "type": "doc",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A ten-minute ritual for evenings when your body has been in service all day. Ten minutes that are only yours before it starts again."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "What you'll need"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "A room with a door that closes. Ten minutes."}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "The practice"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Prepare"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Close the door. It doesn't have to be the bathroom. Any room where you will not be followed. Sit or lie down on the floor or bed. No phone."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Release (repeat x3)"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "blockquote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I am ready to release all of the energy that came into my body today that wasn't mine. I release it now. I release it now. I release it now."}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Allow (repeat x3)"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "blockquote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "I am ready to align with and allow the feeling of being alone in my own body. I allow it now. I allow it now. I allow it now."}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Integrate"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Take five slow breaths. On each exhale, let the body get a little heavier. You don't have to do anything for the next ten minutes."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 3},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Anchor"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "blockquote",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "This body is mine."}]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Say it once, quietly."}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "When the ten minutes are up, open the door and carry on. The short reclaim is enough."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {"level": 2},
        "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from"}]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "By homemade.education. The release and allow structure draws on Rebecca's book The Money Zone."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  }
}
